  "subject": "Pause/Abort API logic for Camunda process",
  "commit_message": "Pause/Abort API logic for Camunda process\n\n- Implemented logic to Pause/Abort Camunda process.\n- Pause will Stop all process instances currently InProgress state.\n- Paused process can be later Resumed, using the Request ID\n- Abort cancel/terminates all process instances currently InProgress state.\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4171\nChange-ID: I73f97f256a817d403f92f8d905dcd0047b8a0806\nSigned-off-by: Ajaj Ahmad <ajaj.ahmad@techmahindra.com>\n",
